oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Unidentified boy
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: This image of an unidentified boy is from an old photograph album found at an estate sale. He wears a plaid dress, without a hoop, and saque coat, identical to th clothing worn by the girl, perhaps his sister, in wils005.; The children in wils003, wils004, wils005, wils006 appear to have been photographed in the same studio.
